::RebelYell::

Recent events had been very confusing to RebelYell.
There were many things to process. Last he remembered,
he was aboard a ship sent on a wild goose chase to
find and rescue Optimus Primal and his crew of morons
onboard the Axalon. He had known Primal and was never
impressed with him or his crew.Now he wakes up in a
stasis pod on an unfamiliar planet with no idea what
happened to his ship or how long he had been drifting
in space before he got here.Now to top it all off he
finds himself bringing spare parts to repair the Ark,
the most legendary ship in Cybertron history, with the
Autobots and Decepticons lying in stasis.In his years
as a soldier, he learned to expect the unexpected, but
nothing could've prepared him for this. He had a
feeling he wasnt going to like this planet much.
